<p>Hello! This week I released <a href="https://flathub.org/apps/net.krafting.SemantiK">SemantiK</a>. It&rsquo;s a word-game where you need to find a secret word, similar to Cémantix or Semantle. The default language model is in French, but you can use and import your own !</p>
<p>It is available on <a href="https://flathub.org/apps/net.krafting.SemantiK">Flathub</a>

